        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Sharp metal jaws wind tightly into the pressure plate mechanism of this snare. When triggered, the jaws clamp shut and spin, damaging limbs in the process. The snare deals [[/r {10d8}[piercing]]]{10d8 piercing damage} to the first creature to enter the square; that creature must attempt a @Check[type:reflex|dc:33|name:Rending Snare|traits:consumable,kobold,mechanical,snare,trap|showDC:all] save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage and is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Flat-Footed]{Flat-Footed} until the end of its next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage plus [[/r {2d6}[persistent,bleed]]] @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Persistent Damage]{Persistent Bleed Damage}, and it becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Clumsy]{Clumsy 2} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage plus [[/r {4d6}[persistent,bleed]]] persistent bleed damage, and it becomes clumsy 2 for 1 minute.</p>"
        },
